---
// Demo showing responsive images with srcset support
---

<section class="flex flex-col gap-m">
  <h3>Responsive Images with srcset</h3>
  
  <div class="grid two-col">
    <cn-card 
      title="Standard Image"
      noun="camera"
      cover="https://picsum.photos/800/450">
      <p>Single image source (no srcset)</p>
    </cn-card>

    <cn-card 
      title="Responsive Image"
      noun="camera"
      cover="https://picsum.photos/800/450"
      srcset="https://picsum.photos/400/225 400w, https://picsum.photos/800/450 800w, https://picsum.photos/1600/900 1600w"
      sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 800px">
      <p>With srcset for optimal loading</p>
    </cn-card>
  </div>

  <div class="callout info">
    <p><strong>Tip:</strong> Open DevTools and check the Network tab while resizing your browser window. 
    The card with srcset will load different image sizes based on viewport width.</p>
  </div>
</section>
